ing\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of the mobilization, Le Revers de la M\\u00e9daille issueda joint statementon behalf of the wider coalition in the major French newspaperLib\\u00e9rationtitled, \\\"Inclusive, Popular, Carbon-neutral Olympics?\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1114, \"end\": 1120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revers\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Revers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revers\"}, {\"begin\": 1205, \"end\": 1211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9995125357511017, \"rank\": 0.0002803177388804468, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mobilization\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"joint statementon behalf\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"the wider coalition\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \", \\\"Inclusive, Popular, Carbon-neutral Olympics\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No Way!\\\"\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1293, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No Way\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In their scathing missive, they slammed Olympic organizers and elected officials for a slew of false pledges.\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their scathing missive\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1319}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic organizers\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1352}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"a slew\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"false pledges\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We see that the Olympic Games are profoundly disrupting the lives o